

{"id":2318,"date":"2023-04-14T11:04:31","date_gmt":"2023-04-14T04:04:31","guid":{"rendered":"https:\/\/tnt.locdt.site\/staging\/?p=2318"},"modified":"2023-07-20T14:57:00","modified_gmt":"2023-07-20T07:57:00","slug":"5-ly-do-nen-tap-luyen-cung-huan-luyen-vien-ca-nhan","status":"publish","type":"post","link":"https:\/\/thenewgym.vn\/5-ly-do-nen-tap-luyen-cung-huan-luyen-vien-ca-nhan\/","title":{"rendered":"5 l\u00fd do n\u00ean t\u1eadp luy\u1ec7n c\u00f9ng hu\u1ea5n luy\u1ec7n vi\u00ean c\u00e1 nh\u00e2n"},"content":{"rendered":"<p><span style=\"color: #ffffff; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;\">T\u1eadp luy\u1ec7n c\u00f9ng Hu\u1ea5n luy\u1ec7n vi\u00ean c\u00e1 nh\u00e2n, T\u1eadp c\u00f9ng PT, T\u1eadp luy\u1ec7n c\u00f9ng PT<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Nhi\u1ec1u kh\u00e1ch h\u00e0ng t\u00ecm \u0111\u1ebfn <\/span><b>hu\u1ea5n luy\u1ec7n vi\u00ean c\u00e1 nh\u00e2n<\/b><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"> (personal trainer hay fitness trainer) v\u00ec nhi\u1ec1u m\u1ee5c \u0111\u00edch kh\u00e1c nhau. Cho d\u00f9 b\u1ea1n mu\u1ed1n <a href=\"https:\/\/thenewgym.vn\/5-phuong-phap-giam-can-khoa-hoc-ban-nen-biet\/\">gi\u1ea3m c\u00e2n<\/a>, <a href=\"https:\/\/thenewgym.vn\/5-cach-de-duy-tri-khoi-luong-co-bap\/\">duy tr\u00ec c\u01a1 b\u1eafp<\/a>, l\u1ea5y l\u1ea1i v\u00f3c d\u00e1ng hay mu\u1ed1n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c<\/span><a href=\"https:\/\/thenewgym.vn\/ho-tro-tap-luyen\/\"> <span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">h\u1ed7 tr\u1ee3 t\u1eadp luy\u1ec7n<\/span><\/a><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">, l\u00ean l\u1ecbch tr\u00ecnh \u0103n u\u1ed1ng khoa h\u1ecdc,&#8230; hu\u1ea5n luy\u1ec7n vi\u00ean c\u00e1 nh\u00e2n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u1ed3ng h\u00e0nh tuy\u1ec7t v\u1eddi.<\/span><\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;\">Nh\u01b0ng \u0111\u00f4i khi, m\u1ecdi ng\u01b0\u1eddi th\u1eadn tr\u1ecdng khi \u0111\u1ea7u t\u01b0 v\u00e0o m\u1ed9t hu\u1ea5n luy\u1ec7n vi\u00ean c\u00e1 nh\u00e2n. Chi ph\u00ed c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1; m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 ng\u01b0\u1eddi c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 c\u1ea3m th\u1ea5y s\u1ee3 h\u00e3i khi l\u00e0m vi\u1ec7c v\u1edbi m\u1ed9t chuy\u00ean gia. Tuy nhi\u00ean, c\u00e1c chuy\u00ean gia th\u1ec3 d\u1ee5c \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ch\u1ee9ng nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e0o t\u1ea1o \u0111\u1ec3 l\u00e0m vi\u1ec7c v\u1edbi kh\u00e1ch h\u00e0ng thu\u1ed9c m\u1ecdi th\u00e0nh ph\u1ea7n v\u00e0 tr\u00ecnh \u0111\u1ed9 th\u1ec3 ch\u1ea5t.<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">N\u1ebfu b\u1ea1n \u0111ang b\u1eaft \u0111\u1ea7u m\u1ed9t ch\u01b0\u01a1ng tr\u00ecnh t\u1eadp th\u1ec3 d\u1ee5c ho\u1eb7c kh\u00f4ng th\u1ea5y k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 v\u1edbi l\u1ecbch tr\u00ecnh t\u1eadp luy\u1ec7n hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh, hu\u1ea5n luy\u1ec7n vi\u00ean c\u00e1 nh\u00e2n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 l\u00e0 l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn t\u1ed1t nh\u1ea5t cho b\u1ea1n. D\u01b0\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 5 l\u00fd do t\u1ea1i sao b\u1ea1n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 mu\u1ed1n thu\u00ea m\u1ed9t <\/span><b>hu\u1ea5n luy\u1ec7n vi\u00ean c\u00e1 nh\u00e2n.<\/b><\/span><\/p>\n<h2><span style=\"font-size: 18pt; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; color: #00a2c4;\"><b><br \/>\nHu\u1ea5n luy\u1ec7n vi\u00ean c\u00e1 nh\u00e2n l\u00e0m g\u00ec?<\/b><\/span><\/h2>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;\">Hu\u1ea5n luy\u1ec7n vi\u00ean c\u00e1 nh\u00e2n l\u00e0m vi\u1ec7c tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp v\u1edbi b\u1ea1n \u0111\u1ec3 gi\u00fap thi\u1ebft k\u1ebf m\u1ed9t ch\u1ebf \u0111\u1ed9 t\u1eadp luy\u1ec7n h\u1ea5p d\u1eabn, gi\u00fap b\u1ea1n gi\u1eef d\u00e1ng, \u0111\u1ea3m b\u1ea3o b\u1ea1n \u0111ang t\u1eadp luy\u1ec7n an to\u00e0n cho t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 c\u00e1c nh\u00f3m c\u01a1 c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh,&#8230;. Tr\u00e1ch nhi\u1ec7m g\u1eb7p g\u1ee1 hu\u1ea5n luy\u1ec7n vi\u00ean c\u1ee7a b\u1ea1n trong m\u1ed9t cu\u1ed9c h\u1eb9n \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1ecbnh c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 gi\u00fap b\u1ea1n \u0111i \u0111\u00fang h\u01b0\u1edbng v\u00e0 \u0111\u1ea1t \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh. Hu\u1ea5n luy\u1ec7n vi\u00ean c\u00e1 nh\u00e2n l\u00e0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u1ed3ng h\u00e0nh tuy\u1ec7t v\u1eddi cho nh\u1eefng ng\u01b0\u1eddi m\u1edbi b\u1eaft \u0111\u1ea7u c\u1ea7n tr\u1ee3 gi\u00fap c\u0169ng nh\u01b0 cho nh\u1eefng ng\u01b0\u1eddi t\u1eadp th\u1ec3 d\u1ee5c d\u00e0y d\u1eb7n h\u01a1n mu\u1ed1n th\u00fac \u0111\u1ea9y b\u1ea3n th\u00e2n h\u01a1n n\u1eefa.<\/span><\/p>\n<h2><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 18pt; color: #00a2c4;\"><b><br \/>\n5 l\u00fd do n\u00ean t\u1eadp luy\u1ec7n c\u00f9ng hu\u1ea5n luy\u1ec7n vi\u00ean c\u00e1 nh\u00e2n<\/b><\/span><\/h2>\n<ol>\n<li><span style=\"font-weight: 400; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;\">\u0110\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 ch\u01b0\u01a1ng tr\u00ecnh v\u00e0 m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i c\u1ee7a b\u1ea1n<\/span><\/li>\n<li><span style=\"font-weight: 400; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;\">Gi\u00fap b\u1ea1n duy tr\u00ec \u0111\u1ed9ng l\u1ef1c v\u00e0 ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c th\u00fac \u0111\u1ea9y<\/span><\/li>\n<li><span style=\"font-weight: 400; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;\">Cung c\u1ea5p l\u1eddi khuy\u00ean gi\u00e1o d\u1ee5c<\/span><\/li>\n<li><span style=\"font-weight: 400; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;\">B\u1ea1n kh\u00f4ng bi\u1ebft b\u1eaft \u0111\u1ea7u t\u1eeb \u0111\u00e2u<\/span><\/li>\n<li><span style=\"font-weight: 400; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;\">B\u1ea1n c\u1ea3m th\u1ea5y nh\u00e0m ch\u00e1n v\u1edbi vi\u1ec7c t\u1eadp luy\u1ec7n c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh<\/span><\/li>\n<\/ol>\n<h2><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;\"><b><br \/>\n\u0110\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 ch\u01b0\u01a1ng tr\u00ecnh v\u00e0 m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i c\u1ee7a b\u1ea1n<\/b><\/span><\/h2>\n<figure id=\"attachment_4793\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-4793\" style=\"width: 2048px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"wp-image-4793 size-full\" src=\"https:\/\/thenewgym.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/04\/danh-gia-chuong-trinh-va-muc-tieu-hien-tai-cua-ban.png\" alt=\"Hu\u1ea5n luy\u1ec7n vi\u00ean c\u00e1 nh\u00e2n, T\u1eadp c\u00f9ng PT, T\u1eadp Gym v\u1edbi PT\" width=\"2048\" height=\"1040\" srcset=\"https:\/\/thenewgym.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/04\/danh-gia-chuong-trinh-va-muc-tieu-hien-tai-cua-ban.png 2048w, https:\/\/thenewgym.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/04\/danh-gia-chuong-trinh-va-muc-tieu-hien-tai-cua-ban-300x152.png 300w, https:\/\/thenewgym.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/04\/danh-gia-chuong-trinh-va-muc-tieu-hien-tai-cua-ban-1024x520.png 1024w, https:\/\/thenewgym.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/04\/danh-gia-chuong-trinh-va-muc-tieu-hien-tai-cua-ban-768x390.png 768w, https:\/\/thenewgym.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/04\/danh-gia-chuong-trinh-va-muc-tieu-hien-tai-cua-ban-1536x780.png 1536w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 2048px) 100vw, 2048px\" \/><figcaption id=\"caption-attachment-4793\" class=\"wp-caption-text\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">\u0110\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 ch\u01b0\u01a1ng tr\u00ecnh v\u00e0 m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i c\u1ee7a b\u1ea1n<\/span><\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;\">B\u1eb1ng c\u00e1ch xem x\u00e9t nh\u1eefng g\u00ec b\u1ea1n \u0111ang l\u00e0m, hu\u1ea5n luy\u1ec7n vi\u00ean c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 \u0111\u1ec1 xu\u1ea5t c\u00e1c c\u00e1ch thay \u0111\u1ed5i ho\u1eb7c \u0111i\u1ec1u ch\u1ec9nh qu\u00e1 tr\u00ecnh t\u1eadp luy\u1ec7n c\u1ee7a b\u1ea1n \u0111\u1ec3 ch\u00fang hi\u1ec7u qu\u1ea3 v\u00e0 hi\u1ec7u qu\u1ea3 h\u01a1n. M\u1ed9t hu\u1ea5n luy\u1ec7n vi\u00ean c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 gi\u00fap x\u00e1c \u0111\u1ecbnh xem m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau c\u1ee7a b\u1ea1n c\u00f3 th\u1ef1c t\u1ebf hay kh\u00f4ng.<\/span><\/p>\n<h2><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;\"><b><br \/>\nGi\u00fap b\u1ea1n duy tr\u00ec \u0111\u1ed9ng l\u1ef1c v\u00e0 ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c th\u00fac \u0111\u1ea9y<\/b><\/span><\/h2>\n<figure id=\"attachment_4803\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-4803\" style=\"width: 2048px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"wp-image-4803 size-full\" src=\"https:\/\/thenewgym.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/04\/giup-ban-duy-tri-dong-luc-va-tiep-tuc-thuc-day-2.png\" alt=\"Hu\u1ea5n luy\u1ec7n vi\u00ean c\u00e1 nh\u00e2n, T\u1eadp c\u00f9ng PT, T\u1eadp Gym v\u1edbi PT\" width=\"2048\" height=\"1040\" srcset=\"https:\/\/thenewgym.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/04\/giup-ban-duy-tri-dong-luc-va-tiep-tuc-thuc-day-2.png 2048w, https:\/\/thenewgym.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/04\/giup-ban-duy-tri-dong-luc-va-tiep-tuc-thuc-day-2-300x152.png 300w, https:\/\/thenewgym.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/04\/giup-ban-duy-tri-dong-luc-va-tiep-tuc-thuc-day-2-1024x520.png 1024w, https:\/\/thenewgym.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/04\/giup-ban-duy-tri-dong-luc-va-tiep-tuc-thuc-day-2-768x390.png 768w, https:\/\/thenewgym.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/04\/giup-ban-duy-tri-dong-luc-va-tiep-tuc-thuc-day-2-1536x780.png 1536w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 2048px) 100vw, 2048px\" \/><figcaption id=\"caption-attachment-4803\" class=\"wp-caption-text\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">Gi\u00fap b\u1ea1n duy tr\u00ec \u0111\u1ed9ng l\u1ef1c v\u00e0 ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c th\u00fac \u0111\u1ea9y<\/span><\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;\">Hu\u1ea5n luy\u1ec7n vi\u00ean gi\u00fap b\u1ea1n duy tr\u00ec \u0111\u1ed9ng l\u1ef1c \u0111\u1ec3 t\u1eadp luy\u1ec7n. M\u1ecdi ng\u01b0\u1eddi th\u01b0\u1eddng kh\u00f4ng nh\u00ecn th\u1ea5y k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 v\u00ec h\u1ecd kh\u00f4ng l\u00e0m vi\u1ec7c ch\u0103m ch\u1ec9 h\u1ebft m\u1ee9c c\u00f3 th\u1ec3.<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;\">B\u1ea1n r\u1ea5t d\u1ec5 ch\u1ec3nh m\u1ea3ng khi \u1edf m\u1ed9t m\u00ecnh, nh\u01b0ng c\u00f3 ai \u0111\u00f3 th\u00e1ch th\u1ee9c b\u1ea1n (v\u00e0 c\u1ed5 v\u0169 b\u1ea1n) c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 t\u1ea1o ra s\u1ef1 kh\u00e1c bi\u1ec7t. Ng\u01b0\u1eddi hu\u1ea5n luy\u1ec7n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 gi\u00fap b\u1ea1n \u0111\u1eb7t m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau h\u00e0ng tu\u1ea7n, sau \u0111\u00f3 ki\u1ec3m tra th\u01b0\u1eddng xuy\u00ean \u0111\u1ec3 xem b\u1ea1n \u0111ang l\u00e0m nh\u01b0 th\u1ebf n\u00e0o, gi\u00fap b\u1ea1n c\u00f3 \u0111\u1ed9ng l\u1ef1c v\u00e0 th\u00fac \u0111\u1ea9y m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh.<\/span><\/p>\n<p>&nbsp;<\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;\"><b>Cung c\u1ea5p l\u1eddi khuy\u00ean gi\u00e1o d\u1ee5c<\/b><\/span><\/p>\n<figure id=\"attachment_4801\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-4801\" style=\"width: 2048px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"wp-image-4801 size-full\" src=\"https:\/\/thenewgym.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/04\/cung-cap-loi-khuyen-giao-duc-2.png\" alt=\"Hu\u1ea5n luy\u1ec7n vi\u00ean c\u00e1 nh\u00e2n, T\u1eadp c\u00f9ng PT, T\u1eadp Gym v\u1edbi PT\" width=\"2048\" height=\"1040\" srcset=\"https:\/\/thenewgym.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/04\/cung-cap-loi-khuyen-giao-duc-2.png 2048w, https:\/\/thenewgym.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/04\/cung-cap-loi-khuyen-giao-duc-2-300x152.png 300w, https:\/\/thenewgym.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/04\/cung-cap-loi-khuyen-giao-duc-2-1024x520.png 1024w, https:\/\/thenewgym.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/04\/cung-cap-loi-khuyen-giao-duc-2-768x390.png 768w, https:\/\/thenewgym.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/04\/cung-cap-loi-khuyen-giao-duc-2-1536x780.png 1536w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 2048px) 100vw, 2048px\" \/><figcaption id=\"caption-attachment-4801\" class=\"wp-caption-text\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">Cung c\u1ea5p l\u1eddi khuy\u00ean gi\u00e1o d\u1ee5c<\/span><\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;\">Cho d\u00f9 b\u1ea1n mu\u1ed1n h\u1ecdc c\u00e1ch n\u00e2ng t\u1ea1 \u0111\u00fang c\u00e1ch hay t\u1eadp m\u1ed9t b\u00e0i t\u1eadp m\u1edbi, hu\u1ea5n luy\u1ec7n vi\u00ean l\u00e0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi c\u00f3 nhi\u1ec1u ki\u1ebfn \u200b\u200bth\u1ee9c. V\u00ed d\u1ee5: b\u1ea1n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 ngh\u0129 r\u1eb1ng m\u00ecnh c\u1ea7n t\u1eadp trung v\u00e0o tim m\u1ea1ch \u0111\u1ec3 gi\u1ea3m c\u00e2n , nh\u01b0ng b\u1ea1n c\u0169ng c\u1ea7n t\u1eadp luy\u1ec7n s\u1ee9c m\u1ea1nh v\u00e0 t\u1eadp luy\u1ec7n c\u1ed1t l\u00f5i, 1 v\u00e0 hu\u1ea5n luy\u1ec7n vi\u00ean c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 gi\u00fap b\u1ea1n l\u1eadp k\u1ebf ho\u1ea1ch.<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;\">B\u1ea1n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3\u2014ch\u1ec9 l\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng theo c\u00e1ch b\u1ea1n mong \u0111\u1ee3i. B\u1ea1n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 t\u0103ng c\u01a1 v\u00e0 gi\u1ea3m m\u1ee1, thay \u0111\u1ed5i th\u00e0nh ph\u1ea7n c\u01a1 th\u1ec3 trong khi c\u00e2n n\u1eb7ng kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u1ed5i. M\u1eb7c d\u00f9 \u0111i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y hi\u1ebfm khi x\u1ea3y ra \u0111\u1ed1i v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u00e3 t\u1eadp luy\u1ec7n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c m\u1ed9t th\u1eddi gian, nh\u01b0ng \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 hi\u1ec7n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng th\u01b0\u1eddng xuy\u00ean x\u1ea3y ra v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng ng\u01b0\u1eddi m\u1edbi t\u1eadp.<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;\">M\u1ed9t hu\u1ea5n luy\u1ec7n vi\u00ean c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 nh\u00ecn th\u1ea5y ho\u00e0n c\u1ea3nh c\u1ee7a b\u1ea1n r\u00f5 r\u00e0ng h\u01a1n t\u1eeb b\u00ean ngo\u00e0i v\u00e0 cung c\u1ea5p cho b\u1ea1n m\u1ed9t g\u00f3c nh\u00ecn m\u1edbi.<\/span><\/p>\n<h2><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;\"><b><br \/>\nB\u1ea1n kh\u00f4ng bi\u1ebft b\u1eaft \u0111\u1ea7u t\u1eeb \u0111\u00e2u<\/b><\/span><\/h2>\n<figure id=\"attachment_4789\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-4789\" style=\"width: 2048px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"wp-image-4789 size-full\" src=\"https:\/\/thenewgym.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/04\/ban-khong-biet-bat-dau-tu-dau.png\" alt=\"Hu\u1ea5n luy\u1ec7n vi\u00ean c\u00e1 nh\u00e2n, T\u1eadp c\u00f9ng PT, T\u1eadp Gym v\u1edbi PT\" width=\"2048\" height=\"1040\" srcset=\"https:\/\/thenewgym.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/04\/ban-khong-biet-bat-dau-tu-dau.png 2048w, https:\/\/thenewgym.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/04\/ban-khong-biet-bat-dau-tu-dau-300x152.png 300w, https:\/\/thenewgym.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/04\/ban-khong-biet-bat-dau-tu-dau-1024x520.png 1024w, https:\/\/thenewgym.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/04\/ban-khong-biet-bat-dau-tu-dau-768x390.png 768w, https:\/\/thenewgym.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/04\/ban-khong-biet-bat-dau-tu-dau-1536x780.png 1536w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 2048px) 100vw, 2048px\" \/><figcaption id=\"caption-attachment-4789\" class=\"wp-caption-text\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">B\u1ea1n kh\u00f4ng bi\u1ebft b\u1eaft \u0111\u1ea7u t\u1eeb \u0111\u00e2u<\/span><\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;\">Ch\u00fang ta kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i sinh ra \u0111\u00e3 bi\u1ebft c\u00e1ch t\u1eadp th\u1ec3 d\u1ee5c ho\u1eb7c c\u00e1ch thi\u1ebft k\u1ebf m\u1ed9t ch\u01b0\u01a1ng tr\u00ecnh ho\u00e0n ch\u1ec9nh bao g\u1ed3m t\u1eadp tim m\u1ea1ch , t\u1eadp t\u1ea1 v\u00e0 r\u00e8n luy\u1ec7n s\u1ef1 linh ho\u1ea1t , nh\u1eefng b\u00e0i t\u1eadp c\u1ee5 th\u1ec3 n\u00e0o c\u1ea7n th\u1ef1c hi\u1ec7n cho t\u1eebng ch\u01b0\u01a1ng tr\u00ecnh \u0111\u00f3 v\u00e0 c\u00e1ch ph\u00f9 h\u1ee3p v\u1edbi l\u1ecbch tr\u00ecnh b\u1eadn r\u1ed9n. \u0110\u1ed1i m\u1eb7t v\u1edbi nhi\u1ec7m v\u1ee5 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 c\u1ea3m th\u1ea5y cho\u00e1ng ng\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ebfn n\u1ed7i b\u1ea1n kh\u00f4ng l\u00e0m g\u00ec c\u1ea3.<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;\">M\u1ed9t hu\u1ea5n luy\u1ec7n vi\u00ean c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 gi\u00fap b\u1ea1n v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng \u0111i\u1ec1u c\u01a1 b\u1ea3n. C\u00e1c b\u00e0i t\u1eadp b\u1ea1n th\u1ef1c hi\u1ec7n ph\u1ea3i d\u1ef1a tr\u00ean nguy\u00ean t\u1eafc FITT : B\u1ea1n ch\u1ecdn t\u1ea7n su\u1ea5t , c\u01b0\u1eddng \u0111\u1ed9 , th\u1eddi gian v\u00e0 lo\u1ea1i b\u00e0i t\u1eadp v\u00e0 v\u1eadn d\u1ee5ng c\u00e1c y\u1ebfu t\u1ed1 n\u00e0y theo th\u1eddi gian.<\/span><\/p>\n<h2><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;\"><b><br \/>\nB\u1ea1n c\u1ea3m th\u1ea5y nh\u00e0m ch\u00e1n v\u1edbi vi\u1ec7c t\u1eadp luy\u1ec7n c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh<\/b><\/span><\/h2>\n<figure id=\"attachment_4787\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-4787\" style=\"width: 2048px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"wp-image-4787 size-full\" src=\"https:\/\/thenewgym.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/04\/ban-cam-thay-nham-chan-voi-viec-tap-luyen-cua-minh.png\" alt=\"Hu\u1ea5n luy\u1ec7n vi\u00ean c\u00e1 nh\u00e2n, T\u1eadp c\u00f9ng PT, T\u1eadp Gym v\u1edbi PT\" width=\"2048\" height=\"1040\" srcset=\"https:\/\/thenewgym.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/04\/ban-cam-thay-nham-chan-voi-viec-tap-luyen-cua-minh.png 2048w, https:\/\/thenewgym.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/04\/ban-cam-thay-nham-chan-voi-viec-tap-luyen-cua-minh-300x152.png 300w, https:\/\/thenewgym.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/04\/ban-cam-thay-nham-chan-voi-viec-tap-luyen-cua-minh-1024x520.png 1024w, https:\/\/thenewgym.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/04\/ban-cam-thay-nham-chan-voi-viec-tap-luyen-cua-minh-768x390.png 768w, https:\/\/thenewgym.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/04\/ban-cam-thay-nham-chan-voi-viec-tap-luyen-cua-minh-1536x780.png 1536w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 2048px) 100vw, 2048px\" \/><figcaption id=\"caption-attachment-4787\" class=\"wp-caption-text\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">B\u1ea1n c\u1ea3m th\u1ea5y nh\u00e0m ch\u00e1n v\u1edbi vi\u1ec7c t\u1eadp luy\u1ec7n c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh<\/span><\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<p><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">N\u1ebfu b\u1ea1n l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t ng\u01b0\u1eddi t\u1eadp th\u1ec3 d\u1ee5c c\u00f3 kinh nghi\u1ec7m, b\u1ea1n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 kh\u00f4ng c\u00e2n nh\u1eafc l\u00e0m vi\u1ec7c v\u1edbi m\u1ed9t <\/span><b>hu\u1ea5n luy\u1ec7n vi\u00ean c\u00e1 nh\u00e2n<\/b><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">. Tuy nhi\u00ean, n\u00f3 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn tuy\u1ec7t v\u1eddi n\u1ebfu b\u1ea1n c\u1ea7n s\u1ef1 \u0111a d\u1ea1ng trong qu\u00e1 tr\u00ecnh t\u1eadp luy\u1ec7n c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh.<\/span><\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;\">R\u1ea5t d\u1ec5 r\u01a1i v\u00e0o l\u1ed1i m\u00f2n t\u1eadp luy\u1ec7n, l\u1eb7p \u0111i l\u1eb7p l\u1ea1i c\u00f9ng m\u1ed9t b\u00e0i t\u1eadp. \u0110i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y kh\u00f4ng ch\u1ec9 nh\u00e0m ch\u00e1n; n\u00f3 c\u0169ng c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 d\u1eabn \u0111\u1ebfn t\u00ecnh tr\u1ea1ng gi\u1ea3m c\u00e2n kh\u00f4ng \u1ed5n \u0111\u1ecbnh , ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng do s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng qu\u00e1 m\u1ee9c v\u00e0 ki\u1ec7t s\u1ee9c.<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;\">N\u1ebfu b\u1ea1n \u0111\u00e3 am hi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 t\u1eadp luy\u1ec7n, b\u1ea1n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 c\u00e2n nh\u1eafc vi\u1ec7c thu\u00ea m\u1ed9t hu\u1ea5n luy\u1ec7n vi\u00ean c\u00e1 nh\u00e2n \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t g\u00f3c nh\u00ecn m\u1edbi m\u1ebb trong khi ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c th\u1eed th\u00e1ch b\u1ea1n h\u01b0\u1edbng t\u1edbi m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh b\u1eb1ng con m\u1eaft kh\u00e1ch quan.<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;\">H\u1ecd c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 th\u1ea5y c\u00e1c l\u0129nh v\u1ef1c trong ch\u01b0\u01a1ng tr\u00ecnh c\u1ee7a b\u1ea1n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111i\u1ec1u ch\u1ec9nh \u0111\u1ec3 l\u00e0m cho vi\u1ec7c t\u1eadp luy\u1ec7n c\u1ee7a b\u1ea1n tr\u1edf n\u00ean th\u00fa v\u1ecb h\u01a1n, th\u1eed th\u00e1ch h\u01a1n ho\u1eb7c th\u00fa v\u1ecb h\u01a1n. M\u1ed9t hu\u1ea5n luy\u1ec7n vi\u00ean s\u1ebd xem x\u00e9t hi\u1ec7u su\u1ea5t t\u1eadp luy\u1ec7n c\u1ee7a b\u1ea1n v\u00e0 cho b\u1ea1n bi\u1ebft v\u1ec1 b\u1ea5t k\u1ef3 l\u0129nh v\u1ef1c n\u00e0o b\u1ea1n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 c\u1ea3i thi\u1ec7n ho\u1eb7c n\u01a1i b\u1ea1n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 th\u00fac \u0111\u1ea9y b\u1ea3n th\u00e2n ch\u0103m ch\u1ec9 h\u01a1n m\u1ed9t ch\u00fat.<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;\">Hu\u1ea5n luy\u1ec7n vi\u00ean c\u00f3 kinh nghi\u1ec7m trong nhi\u1ec1u lo\u1ea1i h\u00ecnh t\u1eadp luy\u1ec7n kh\u00e1c nhau. T\u00ecm ai \u0111\u00f3 \u0111\u1ec3 ch\u1ec9 cho b\u1ea1n nh\u1eefng s\u1ee3i d\u00e2y n\u1ebfu b\u1ea1n mu\u1ed1n th\u1eed. \u0110i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 c\u00f3 ngh\u0129a l\u00e0 luy\u1ec7n t\u1eadp ng\u1eaft qu\u00e3ng c\u01b0\u1eddng \u0111\u1ed9 cao (luy\u1ec7n t\u1eadp Tabata ), c\u00e1c ph\u01b0\u01a1ng ph\u00e1p r\u00e8n luy\u1ec7n s\u1ee9c m\u1ea1nh kh\u00e1c nhau, bao g\u1ed3m luy\u1ec7n t\u1eadp supersets\u00a0 v\u00e0 kim t\u1ef1 th\u00e1p.<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;\">M\u1ed9t hu\u1ea5n luy\u1ec7n vi\u00ean \u0111\u01b0a ra m\u1ed9t quan \u0111i\u1ec3m m\u1edbi m\u1ebb v\u00e0 nh\u1eefng \u00fd t\u01b0\u1edfng m\u1edbi \u0111\u1ec3 th\u1eed th\u00e1ch c\u01a1 th\u1ec3 v\u00e0 t\u00e2m tr\u00ed c\u1ee7a b\u1ea1n. Ngay c\u1ea3 khi b\u1ea1n ch\u1ec9 c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t v\u00e0i bu\u1ed5i t\u1eadp ho\u1eb7c g\u1eb7p nhau v\u00e0i tu\u1ea7n m\u1ed9t l\u1ea7n, th\u00ec vi\u1ec7c c\u00f3 c\u00e1c b\u00e0i t\u1eadp v\u00e0 thi\u1ebft b\u1ecb t\u1eadp th\u1ec3 d\u1ee5c m\u1edbi \u0111\u1ec3 th\u1eed c\u0169ng r\u1ea5t th\u00fa v\u1ecb.<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">B\u1ea1n s\u1ebd th\u1ea5y kh\u00f3 m\u00e0 bu\u00f4ng l\u01a1i khi hu\u1ea5n luy\u1ec7n vi\u00ean \u0111\u1ee9ng ph\u00eda tr\u00ean b\u1ea3o b\u1ea1n ch\u1ec9 <\/span><i><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">t\u1eadp th\u00eam m\u1ed9t l\u1ea7n n\u1eefa. <\/span><\/i><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">B\u1ea1n th\u1eadm ch\u00ed c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 th\u1ea5y m\u00ecnh c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng \u0111i\u1ec3m m\u1ea1nh ti\u1ec1m \u1ea9n \u0111\u1ec3 khai th\u00e1c, \u0111i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 th\u00fac \u0111\u1ea9y b\u1ea1n nhi\u1ec1u h\u01a1n n\u1eefa.<\/span><\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">V\u1eady t\u1eadp luy\u1ec7n \u1edf \u0111\u00e2u \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00f3 hu\u1ea5n luy\u1ec7n vi\u00ean t\u1ed1t nh\u1ea5t, trung t\u00e2m gym n\u00e0o cung c\u1ea5p hu\u1ea5n luy\u1ec7n vi\u00ean t\u1ed1t,<\/span><a href=\"https:\/\/thenewgym.vn\/dia-diem-tap-gym-tot-nhat-ho-chi-minh\/\"> <span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">\u0111\u1ecba \u0111i\u1ec3m t\u1eadp gym<\/span><\/a><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"> n\u00e0o c\u00f3 hu\u1ea5n luy\u1ec7n vi\u00ean t\u1ed1t, l\u00e0 c\u00e2u h\u1ecfi m\u00e0 nhi\u1ec1u ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u1eb7t ra.<\/span><\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;\">T\u1ea1i The New Gym, ch\u00fang t\u00f4i cung c\u1ea5p \u0111\u1ed9i ng\u0169 Hu\u1ea5n luy\u1ec7n vi\u00ean chuy\u00ean nghi\u1ec7p, nhi\u1ec7t t\u00ecnh, theo s\u00e1t b\u1ea1n trong qu\u00e1 tr\u00ecnh luy\u1ec7n t\u1eadp, gi\u00fap b\u1ea1n nhanh ch\u00f3ng \u0111\u1ea1t \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau.<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">\u0110\u1ec3 t\u00ecm hi\u1ec3u th\u00eam v\u1ec1 ch\u00ednh s\u00e1ch gi\u00e1, ho\u1eb7c c\u1ea7n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c t\u01b0 v\u1ea5n th\u00eam v\u1ec1 PT, b\u1ea1n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 li\u00ean h\u1ec7 <a href=\"https:\/\/www.facebook.com\/thenewgymvietnam\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Fanpage<\/a><\/span><a href=\"https:\/\/www.facebook.com\/thenewgymvietnam\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\"> <span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">The New Gym<\/span><\/a><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">.<\/span><\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"color: #ffffff; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;\">Hu\u1ea5n luy\u1ec7n vi\u00ean, Hu\u1ea5n luy\u1ec7n vi\u00ean c\u00e1 nh\u00e2n, PT, Personal Trainer<\/span><\/p>\n","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"<p>T\u1eadp luy\u1ec7n c\u00f9ng Hu\u1ea5n luy\u1ec7n vi\u00ean c\u00e1 nh\u00e2n, T\u1eadp c\u00f9ng PT, T\u1eadp luy\u1ec7n c\u00f9ng PT Nhi\u1ec1u kh\u00e1ch h\u00e0ng t\u00ecm \u0111\u1ebfn hu\u1ea5n luy\u1ec7n vi\u00ean c\u00e1 nh\u00e2n (personal trainer hay fitness trainer) v\u00ec nhi\u1ec1u m\u1ee5c \u0111\u00edch kh\u00e1c nhau. Cho d\u00f9 b\u1ea1n mu\u1ed1n gi\u1ea3m c\u00e2n, duy tr\u00ec c\u01a1 b\u1eafp, l\u1ea5y l\u1ea1i v\u00f3c d\u00e1ng hay mu\u1ed1n \u0111\u01b0\u1e